Creating a quick PR&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In Git:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;
The standard procedure is to create a branch, commit your changes, push that branch, and then open a pull request on your hosting platform.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #383A42; background-color: #FAFAFA;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #A0A1A7;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;# Create a new branch&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #4078F2;&quot;&gt;git&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50A14F;&quot;&gt; checkout&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #986801;&quot;&gt; -b&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50A14F;&quot;&gt; my-feature-branch&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #A0A1A7;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;# Make your changes&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #4078F2;&quot;&gt;vim&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50A14F;&quot;&gt; lib&#x2F;edit.ts&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #A0A1A7;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;# Stage and commit your changes&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #4078F2;&quot;&gt;git&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50A14F;&quot;&gt; add .&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #4078F2;&quot;&gt;git&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50A14F;&quot;&gt; commit&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #986801;&quot;&gt; -m&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50A14F;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;My feature&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #A0A1A7;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;# Push the branch to the remote&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #4078F2;&quot;&gt;git&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50A14F;&quot;&gt; push origin my-feature-branch&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #A0A1A7;font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;# Create a pull request&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #4078F2;&quot;&gt;gh&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #50A14F;&quot;&gt; pr create&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
